ff:node10 a ff:Node;
    ff:hasClass ff:MarkdownNode;
    ff:hasName "Input: merged DCAT-AP.de metadata from 3 datasets";
    ff:hasPosX 1402;
    ff:hasPosY -155;
    ff:hasWidth 454;
    ff:hasHeight 286;
    ff:hasValue "3 randomly chosen datasets from open.bydata.de:\n- [Aggregierte Bewegungsdaten mit MoT in München](https://open.bydata.de/datasets/573260013458354176)\n- [Familienstützpunkte im Landkreis Regensburg](https://open.bydata.de/datasets/https-lk-regensburg-bydata-de-dataset-familienstu-tzpunkte)\n- [Buslinien in der Stadt Deggendorf](https://open.bydata.de/datasets/buslinien-deggendorf)\n\nThe links below in the node-titles are the dataset-URIs, which also serve as direct links to the metadata in JSON-LD.\nThe JSON-LD gets converted to Turtle to be able to visualize the triples.\n\n&rarr; *Run it by pressing \"Run\" in the upper left corner.*".
